<h1>Why is DAC inadequate?</h1>
<ul>
<li>
<h2>Decisions are only based on user identity and ownership</h2>
</li>
<li>
<h2>No protection against malicious or flawed software</h2>
</li>
<li>
<h2>Each user has complete discretion over his objects</h2>
</li>
<li>
<h2>Only two major categories of users: administrator and
other</h2>
</li>
<li>
<h2>Many system services and privileged programs must run with
coarse-grained privileges or even full administrator access.</h2>
</li>
</ul>
